items.name: Elegant Hubris
explicitMods:
Commissioned 118540 coins to commemorate Victario
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Eternal Empire
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves better than the past, but that confidence brought about nightmare.

items.name: Forbidden Flesh
explicitMods: Allocates Champion if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flame
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The bodies of those wholly subsumed by the Tangle
continue to merge and mutate and cry out for release...

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: Gain 9% of Maximum Mana as Extra Maximum Energy Shield while affected by Clarity
Unaffected by Enfeeble while affected by Grace
Unaffected by Flammability while affected by Purity of Fire
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: Intuitive Leap
explicitMods: Passives in Radius can be Allocated without being connected to your tree
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The carpenter who picks up a blade is not mad.

items.name: Morbid Sphere
explicitMods: 5% chance to gain Phasing for 4 seconds on Kill
items.descrText: Place into an Abyssal Socket on an Item or into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Champion if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...
